==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: A person's heart is near one's belly.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén xīn gé dù pí

===Idiom===
'''[[人心]][[隔]][[肚皮]]'''

# Keep one's thoughts to oneself.
# Keep one's thoughts close to one's breast.
# To not reveal what one is thinking.

